title: "How to Build a Support Metrics Dashboard That Drives Action, Not Just Reports"
date: "2023-04-03"
summary: "Build a support metrics dashboard that produces action. Design for decisions, not for observation."
coverImage: ""
tags:
  - "Analytics"
